      "metadata": {
        "id": "d593e656"
      },
      "source": [
        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "Now that the Decision Tree Classifier is trained, the next step is to use the trained model to make predictions on the test dataset (`x_test`) to evaluate its performance.\n",
        "\n"
      ],
      "id": "d593e656"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
